(473, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Special:Randomizer', '4 Ways to Make Parsley Tea - wikiHow', 'How to Make Parsley Tea. Parsley tea is an herbal solution often used to treat muscle spasms, improve digestion, enhance urine production, and increase menstrual flow. You can make parsley tea using fresh or dried leaves, roots, or seeds....', '', 0),
