(475, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Arts-and-Entertainment', 'Arts and Entertainment - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Learn to be well read, become a better artist, and sell your own music with wikiHow\'s Arts and Entertainment category. Our articles can help you develop talent in multiple areas and be a good entertainer. Check out how-tos on learning ventriloquism, making your own radio show, becoming a professional storyteller, and more.', '', 0),
(476, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Cars-%26-Other-Vehicles', 'Cars & Other Vehicles - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Check out tips on buying a car and doing basic maintenance on a variety of vehicles with wikiHow\'s Cars &amp; Other Vehicles category. Learn to ride a motorcycle, install a rear-view camera, seal a plastic gas tank, and more with help from our step-by-step articles. If you prefer something other than a car or motorcycle, you can also read articles on topics like choosing a bicycle or sailing a boat!', '', 0),
(477, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Computers-and-Electronics', 'Computers and Electronics - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Do you need to check your hard disk space or put pictures on a flash drive? The 1000+ articles in wikiHow\'s Computers and Electronics category can help. Get information covering a range of platforms and operating systems, from turning on AirPlay to connecting a PC to TV using an HDMI cable. Learn to check your computer\'s system information, wipe a computer clean to start over, and much more.', '', 0),
(478, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Education-and-Communications', 'Education and Communications - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Navigate school as a student, be an effective teacher, or build your future—wikiHow\'s Education and Communications category can help you make yourself smarter no matter where you\'re at in life. Our helpful how-to articles can guide you through improving analytical skills, requesting high school transcripts, conducting workshops, choosing between private and public school, and more.', '', 0),
(479, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Family-Life', 'Family Life - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Need to work through some family problems? Or are you just looking to maximize time spent with your family? wikiHow\'s Family Life articles are here to help! Learn to handle small kids, define family values, develop good parent-child relationships, and more. Building a good family life is a goal within your reach!', '', 0),
(480, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Finance-and-Business', 'Finance and Business - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Be smart with money and learn how to start your own business with wikiHow\'s Finance and Business category. Find expert advice on filing taxes, getting rid of credit card debt, learning accounting, and more. Whether you want to discover how to budget your money or achieve business goals, the road to financial success lies just ahead!', '', 0),
(481, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Food-and-Entertaining', 'Food and Entertaining - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Learn to be a great cook and host a fantastic party with wikiHow\'s Food and Entertaining articles. Whether you\'re planning on serving a full course meal for an event, preparing a romantic dinner for someone special, or using leftovers in creative ways, you can find just the right guide to help. Find advice on garnishing food, dealing with picky eaters, and more.', '', 0),
(482, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Health', 'Health - how to articles from wikiHow', 'The wikiHow Health category has more than 200 how-to guides on keeping yourself healthy and happy. Get expert-reviewed advice on creating a wellness plan, maximizing workout benefits, avoiding unhealthy health-related goals, and more. No matter what your health concerns and questions are, wikiHow can help you take control of your health and live your best life.', '', 0),
(483, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Hobbies-and-Crafts', 'Hobbies and Crafts - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Find a new hobby with the help of wikiHow\'s Hobbies and Crafts category. Depending on your interests, you could try people watching, start your own radio show, learn to inlay wood, or pick from many other ideas! Whether you want to find a low-cost hobby to enjoy or just want to pick a hobby you\'ll stick with, our step-by-step articles can give you plenty of ideas.', '', 0),
(484, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Holidays-and-Traditions', 'Holidays and Traditions - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Celebrate a new holiday or freshen up an old favorite with wikiHow\'s Holidays and Traditions category! Find advice on celebrating religious holidays like Easter, Rosh Hashanah, and Eid ul-Fitr. You can also get tips on dressing for Oktoberfest, discover what it takes to host Thanksgiving dinner, look up new ways to celebrate the New Year, and much more!', '', 0),
(485, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Home-and-Garden', 'Home and Garden - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Are you ready to settle into your first apartment or live completely off the grid? wikiHow’s Home and Garden pages have all the advice you need to decorate your home and plan your ideal garden! Find expert-reviewed advice on how to add a low-cost gym to your home, screen a porch, prepare a new garden bed, and more.', '', 0),
(486, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Personal-Care-and-Style', 'Personal Care and Style - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Look and feel your best with help from wikiHow\'s Personal Care and Style category! Fine-tune your everyday style with articles on how to choose a hair salon, how to be stylish and casual at the same time, how to wake up beautiful, and more. You can also find tips on how to pull off certain styles, like boxy tops or leggings at work!', '', 0),
(487, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Pets-and-Animals', 'Pets and Animals - how to articles from wikiHow', 'With lots of love and care, your pet can become your lifelong friend. wikiHow\'s Pets and Animals category is here to help. Learn how to adopt a new pet and care for your new companion, and get expert advice on the best ways to care for pets of all types. wikiHow can help you bond with your dog, have fun with your cat, keep your pet rat clean, and more.', '', 0),
(488, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Philosophy-and-Religion', 'Philosophy and Religion - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Expand your mind and enhance your beliefs with help from wikiHow\'s Philosophy and Religion category. Increasing your understanding of different religions and philosophies can help you find your own way and appreciate cultural differences between you and others. Get advice on how to talk to God, save yourself, and more with our how-to guides.', '', 0),
(489, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Relationships', 'Relationships - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Build healthy relationships and learn to show more affection with the help of wikiHow\'s Relationships category. Get expert-reviewed advice on moving from dating to a relationship, fighting for a relationship, and more. Whether you want to be an expert at cuddling or just want to know when someone likes you romantically, we\'ve got advice for you!', '', 0),
(490, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Sports-and-Fitness', 'Sports and Fitness - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Start exercising or improve at sports with wikiHow\'s Sports and Fitness category. Choose the right exercise program by checking out our guides on specific goals like gaining flexibility and improving agility. Embrace your athletic side by exploring in-depth guides on a variety of sports, from baseball to bowling.', '', 0),
(491, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Travel', 'Travel - how to articles from wikiHow', 'If you\'re looking to book a hotel room, create a travel budget, or pack a suitcase like a pro, wikiHow\'s Travel articles have got you covered. Our guides will help you choose the perfect travel destination, whether you prefer to plan out your vacations or travel spontaneously. Learn to safely travel the world, be a tourist in your own hometown, and more!', '', 0),
(492, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Work-World', 'Work World - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Navigating the workplace can be tough, but wikiHow\'s Work World category can help you behave professionally and stay motivated at your job. Get expert-reviewed advice on topics ranging from accepting criticism at work to keeping your personal and professional lives separate. Learn to dress business casual, improve soft skills, and become a happier employee.', '', 0),
(493, 'http://www.wikihow.com/Category:Youth', 'Youth - how to articles from wikiHow', 'Being a young person isn\'t always easy, but wikiHow\'s Youth category can help! Find guides no matter what age group you are, from impressing people as a kid to being a mature preteen and taking control of your life as a teen. Learn all about making people want to be your friend, staying out of trouble, figuring out what you want to be when you grow up, and more.', '', 0),
